			"path": "ded5a514-3b2d-420d-b470-d672fd8dee15",
			"cellName": "Flow 1: Configure Component Auto-Importing - vite.config.ts:L68-75",
			"cellId": "ded5a514-3b2d-420d-b470-d672fd8dee15",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-5f65bec1-2206-4255-83bb-917124fc48b5": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-5f65bec1-2206-4255-83bb-917124fc48b5",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "The Vite build process starts by reading `vite.config.ts`. The `unplugin-vue-components` plugin is configured to automatically discover and register Vue components from specified directories.",
			"cellName": "Flow 1: Configure Component Auto-Importing - vite.config.ts:L68-75",
			"cellId": "ded5a514-3b2d-420d-b470-d672fd8dee15",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 68,
			"endLine": 75,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "On-demand Component and API Auto-Importing",
					"simStepId": "5f65bec1-2206-4255-83bb-917124fc48b5"
				}
			]
		},
		"b5aa4dce-0529-43c1-b827-c112e305055f": {
			"path": "b5aa4dce-0529-43c1-b827-c112e305055f",
			"cellName": "Generate Component Type Definitions - components.d.ts:L8-17",
			"cellId": "b5aa4dce-0529-43c1-b827-c112e305055f",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "2579f5e2-adce-4c8a-8817-39e3002e1f06"
		},
		"src/components.d.ts-simstep-9506f028-40e7-482b-9a4a-478e5ea6fcb6": {
			"path": "src/components.d.ts-simstep-9506f028-40e7-482b-9a4a-478e5ea6fcb6",
			"fileName": "components.d.ts",
			"wiki": "Based on the found components, the plugin generates the `src/components.d.ts` file. This file provides global TypeScript definitions for the components, allowing them to be used in templates without explicit imports and with full type support in the IDE.",
			"cellName": "Generate Component Type Definitions - components.d.ts:L8-17",
			"cellId": "b5aa4dce-0529-43c1-b827-c112e305055f",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 8,
			"endLine": 17,
			"parentCellId": "2579f5e2-adce-4c8a-8817-39e3002e1f06",
			"parentPath": "src/components.d.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "On-demand Component and API Auto-Importing",
					"simStepId": "9506f028-40e7-482b-9a4a-478e5ea6fcb6"
				}
			]
		},
		"356d8b73-9faf-4b31-a833-ccca46763127": {
			"path": "356d8b73-9faf-4b31-a833-ccca46763127",
			"cellName": "Build-Time Component Resolution - vite.config.ts:L68-75",
			"cellId": "356d8b73-9faf-4b31-a833-ccca46763127",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-0d7c181e-3eac-4805-9d19-c8d82dd0643a": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-0d7c181e-3eac-4805-9d19-c8d82dd0643a",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "During the Vite build process, the Vue template compiler encounters a tag like `<TheFooter />`. The `unplugin-vue-components` plugin intercepts this, resolves it to the actual file path, and effectively injects `import TheFooter from 'src/components/TheFooter.vue'` behind the scenes before the final code is bundled.",
			"cellName": "Build-Time Component Resolution - vite.config.ts:L68-75",
			"cellId": "356d8b73-9faf-4b31-a833-ccca46763127",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 68,
			"endLine": 75,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "On-demand Component and API Auto-Importing",
					"simStepId": "0d7c181e-3eac-4805-9d19-c8d82dd0643a"
				}
			]
		},
		"8633f810-4638-407c-ba47-34542bbc5baf": {
			"path": "8633f810-4638-407c-ba47-34542bbc5baf",
			"cellName": "Flow 2: Configure API Auto-Importing - vite.config.ts:L46-66",
			"cellId": "8633f810-4638-407c-ba47-34542bbc5baf",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-477b57a4-0018-4b11-8fc5-061e8cf7ad15": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-477b57a4-0018-4b11-8fc5-061e8cf7ad15",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "In `vite.config.ts`, the `unplugin-auto-import` plugin is configured. It's set up to find and globally expose APIs (like `ref` or `computed`) from specified libraries (e.g., 'vue', '@vueuse/core') and custom directories ('src/composables').",
			"cellName": "Flow 2: Configure API Auto-Importing - vite.config.ts:L46-66",
			"cellId": "8633f810-4638-407c-ba47-34542bbc5baf",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 46,
			"endLine": 66,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "On-demand Component and API Auto-Importing",
					"simStepId": "477b57a4-0018-4b11-8fc5-061e8cf7ad15"
				}
			]
		},
		"57a71840-22ad-4e04-a292-3edc6824342c": {
			"path": "57a71840-22ad-4e04-a292-3edc6824342c",
			"cellName": "Generate API Type Definitions - auto-imports.d.ts:L8-9",
			"cellId": "57a71840-22ad-4e04-a292-3edc6824342c",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "b836dbe6-2c48-4b3d-a843-f852ced3b808"
		},
		"src/auto-imports.d.ts-simstep-b04e9b59-4430-4671-b880-3e4a68a6b4cc": {
			"path": "src/auto-imports.d.ts-simstep-b04e9b59-4430-4671-b880-3e4a68a6b4cc",
			"fileName": "auto-imports.d.ts",
			"wiki": "The plugin generates `src/auto-imports.d.ts`, which declares all discovered APIs (e.g., `ref`, `computed`, `useHead`, `useI18n`, `isDark`) as global constants. This provides TypeScript with the necessary type information, enabling autocompletion and preventing 'not defined' errors in the IDE.",
			"cellName": "Generate API Type Definitions - auto-imports.d.ts:L8-9",
			"cellId": "57a71840-22ad-4e04-a292-3edc6824342c",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 8,
			"endLine": 9,
			"parentCellId": "b836dbe6-2c48-4b3d-a843-f852ced3b808",
			"parentPath": "src/auto-imports.d.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "On-demand Component and API Auto-Importing",
					"simStepId": "b04e9b59-4430-4671-b880-3e4a68a6b4cc"
				}
			]
		},
		"6c26b624-d46c-4d74-b3c9-6df238bc9f0c": {
			"path": "6c26b624-d46c-4d74-b3c9-6df238bc9f0c",
			"cellName": "Build-Time Code Transformation - vite.config.ts:L46-66",
			"cellId": "6c26b624-d46c-4d74-b3c9-6df238bc9f0c",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-46ecbd64-0ee2-4bee-a3a1-bebfce34f25d": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-46ecbd64-0ee2-4bee-a3a1-bebfce34f25d",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "When Vite processes a file, the `unplugin-auto-import` plugin scans the code for usage of these global APIs. Upon finding `useI18n`, it transparently injects the necessary `import { useI18n } from 'vue-i18n'` statement at the top of the script. This transformed code is then passed to the rest of the build chain.",
			"cellName": "Build-Time Code Transformation - vite.config.ts:L46-66",
			"cellId": "6c26b624-d46c-4d74-b3c9-6df238bc9f0c",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 46,
			"endLine": 66,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "On-demand Component and API Auto-Importing",
					"simStepId": "46ecbd64-0ee2-4bee-a3a1-bebfce34f25d"
				}
			]
		},
