		"469298e3-fcfe-447a-8cb6-03d2e8a1fd4f": {
			"path": "469298e3-fcfe-447a-8cb6-03d2e8a1fd4f",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Initialize Pinia Instance - pinia.ts:L6-8",
			"cellId": "469298e3-fcfe-447a-8cb6-03d2e8a1fd4f",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e"
		},
		"src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-06968957-b1c7-4a4e-a473-b40c12f0af9a": {
			"path": "src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-06968957-b1c7-4a4e-a473-b40c12f0af9a",
			"fileName": "pinia.ts",
			"wiki": "The application setup process invokes the `install` function, which is a ViteSSG UserModule. Inside this function, a new Pinia instance is created using `createPinia()`.",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Initialize Pinia Instance - pinia.ts:L6-8",
			"cellId": "469298e3-fcfe-447a-8cb6-03d2e8a1fd4f",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 6,
			"endLine": 8,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/pinia.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Integrated State Management with Pinia",
					"simStepId": "06968957-b1c7-4a4e-a473-b40c12f0af9a"
				}
			]
		},
		"fe5e70c8-fc2f-48b1-af40-df874a8ad225": {
			"path": "fe5e70c8-fc2f-48b1-af40-df874a8ad225",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Server-Side State Serialization - pinia.ts:L15-16",
			"cellId": "fe5e70c8-fc2f-48b1-af40-df874a8ad225",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e"
		},
		"src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-036d855a-51ff-4940-943b-23bc4f677d1c": {
			"path": "src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-036d855a-51ff-4940-943b-23bc4f677d1c",
			"fileName": "pinia.ts",
			"wiki": "During Server-Side Generation (SSG), where `isClient` is false, the application's current state is captured from the Pinia instance (`pinia.state.value`) and stored in the `initialState.pinia` object. This object will be serialized by ViteSSG.",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Server-Side State Serialization - pinia.ts:L15-16",
			"cellId": "fe5e70c8-fc2f-48b1-af40-df874a8ad225",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 15,
			"endLine": 16,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/pinia.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Integrated State Management with Pinia",
					"simStepId": "036d855a-51ff-4940-943b-23bc4f677d1c"
				}
			]
		},
		"d62ac2e6-386c-449b-b029-6d3f4cc4ca98": {
			"path": "d62ac2e6-386c-449b-b029-6d3f4cc4ca98",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Client-Side State Hydration - pinia.ts:L12-13",
			"cellId": "d62ac2e6-386c-449b-b029-6d3f4cc4ca98",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e"
		},
		"src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-d34c4c82-4aa8-4cf0-9653-c2ed5f8b4fee": {
			"path": "src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-d34c4c82-4aa8-4cf0-9653-c2ed5f8b4fee",
			"fileName": "pinia.ts",
			"wiki": "When the application boots up in the browser, the `install` function runs again. This time `isClient` is true, and the logic hydrates the new client-side Pinia instance with the state received from the server via `initialState.pinia`.",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Client-Side State Hydration - pinia.ts:L12-13",
			"cellId": "d62ac2e6-386c-449b-b029-6d3f4cc4ca98",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 12,
			"endLine": 13,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/pinia.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Integrated State Management with Pinia",
					"simStepId": "d34c4c82-4aa8-4cf0-9653-c2ed5f8b4fee"
				}
			]
		},
		"c1ba3f9d-1122-4bf7-9a6b-f82911850216": {
			"path": "c1ba3f9d-1122-4bf7-9a6b-f82911850216",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Define User Store - user.ts:L3-31",
			"cellId": "c1ba3f9d-1122-4bf7-9a6b-f82911850216",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "6babaaf0-cc74-4fc9-9511-c2d6a2adb728"
		},
		"src/stores/user.ts-simstep-195c50d2-7e98-4879-87a8-cb05cc474e72": {
			"path": "src/stores/user.ts-simstep-195c50d2-7e98-4879-87a8-cb05cc474e72",
			"fileName": "user.ts",
			"wiki": "The user store is defined in `src/stores/user.ts` using `defineStore`. This function sets up the store's ID ('user'), state (`savedName`, `previousNames`), computed properties (`otherNames`), and actions (`setNewName`). It returns the `useUserStore` composable function.",
			"cellName": "Pinia: Define User Store - user.ts:L3-31",
			"cellId": "c1ba3f9d-1122-4bf7-9a6b-f82911850216",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 3,
