			"fileName": "auto-imports.d.ts",
			"wiki": "Based on the configuration, `unplugin-auto-import` generates a TypeScript declaration file (`src/auto-imports.d.ts`) that globally declares `useUserStore`, providing type safety and editor autocompletion across the project.",
			"cellName": "Vite: Generate Auto-Import Declarations - auto-imports.d.ts:L282",
			"cellId": "0c5faa3c-a18d-449f-a862-870f368013f6",
