		"953ee862-666e-4642-9bc5-f472f068cdd9": {
			"path": "953ee862-666e-4642-9bc5-f472f068cdd9",
			"cellName": "UnoCSS Plugin Registration - vite.config.ts:L79",
			"cellId": "953ee862-666e-4642-9bc5-f472f068cdd9",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-60d48da3-f03b-4750-8b83-5d6616ea5b12": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-60d48da3-f03b-4750-8b83-5d6616ea5b12",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "Inside `vite.config.ts`, the `Unocss()` function is called, which initializes and registers the UnoCSS plugin with Vite. This allows UnoCSS to hook into Vite's build pipeline to scan files and generate CSS.",
			"cellName": "UnoCSS Plugin Registration - vite.config.ts:L79",
			"cellId": "953ee862-666e-4642-9bc5-f472f068cdd9",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 79,
			"endLine": 79,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Efficient Styling with On-Demand Atomic CSS & Icons",
					"simStepId": "60d48da3-f03b-4750-8b83-5d6616ea5b12"
				}
			]
		},
		"3adb4af6-45b1-435a-9161-f1dd244c2ac8": {
			"path": "3adb4af6-45b1-435a-9161-f1dd244c2ac8",
			"cellName": "UnoCSS Configuration Loading - uno.config.ts:L15-27",
			"cellId": "3adb4af6-45b1-435a-9161-f1dd244c2ac8",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "f7702ab9-b209-44eb-90f2-653042bc6568"
		},
		"uno.config.ts-simstep-6c050fbe-c357-4504-82c5-7773eaf0adf8": {
			"path": "uno.config.ts-simstep-6c050fbe-c357-4504-82c5-7773eaf0adf8",
			"fileName": "uno.config.ts",
			"wiki": "The UnoCSS Vite plugin automatically discovers and loads its configuration from `uno.config.ts`. This file defines crucial aspects like presets for utility classes (`presetUno`), icons (`presetIcons`), and custom shortcuts (`icon-btn`).",
			"cellName": "UnoCSS Configuration Loading - uno.config.ts:L15-27",
			"cellId": "3adb4af6-45b1-435a-9161-f1dd244c2ac8",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 15,
			"endLine": 27,
			"parentCellId": "f7702ab9-b209-44eb-90f2-653042bc6568",
			"parentPath": "uno.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Efficient Styling with On-Demand Atomic CSS & Icons",
					"simStepId": "6c050fbe-c357-4504-82c5-7773eaf0adf8"
				}
			]
		},
		"9efed280-90c2-4542-a843-7030d9c4271b": {
			"path": "9efed280-90c2-4542-a843-7030d9c4271b",
			"cellName": "Source File Scanning for CSS Classes - TheFooter.vue:L16-36",
			"cellId": "9efed280-90c2-4542-a843-7030d9c4271b",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "f11c6eff-b35e-4490-8979-0196e1258d8d"
		},
		"src/components/TheFooter.vue-simstep-b72a41e3-5e0e-4c0e-8ccb-be95324d517d": {
			"path": "src/components/TheFooter.vue-simstep-b72a41e3-5e0e-4c0e-8ccb-be95324d517d",
			"fileName": "TheFooter.vue",
			"wiki": "As Vite processes the application's source files, the UnoCSS plugin scans their content to find all used utility classes, icon identifiers, and attributify modes. In this example, it finds `icon-btn` and `i-carbon-campsite` within `TheFooter.vue`.",
			"cellName": "Source File Scanning for CSS Classes - TheFooter.vue:L16-36",
			"cellId": "9efed280-90c2-4542-a843-7030d9c4271b",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 16,
			"endLine": 36,
			"parentCellId": "f11c6eff-b35e-4490-8979-0196e1258d8d",
			"parentPath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Efficient Styling with On-Demand Atomic CSS & Icons",
					"simStepId": "b72a41e3-5e0e-4c0e-8ccb-be95324d517d"
				}
			]
		},
		"02652819-aa39-437a-a6f7-9b605d44708d": {
			"path": "02652819-aa39-437a-a6f7-9b605d44708d",
			"cellName": "On-Demand CSS Generation - uno.config.ts:L16-25",
			"cellId": "02652819-aa39-437a-a6f7-9b605d44708d",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "f7702ab9-b209-44eb-90f2-653042bc6568"
		},
		"uno.config.ts-simstep-782aa577-d8ef-4cf6-9990-dc4c0d5afab3": {
			"path": "uno.config.ts-simstep-782aa577-d8ef-4cf6-9990-dc4c0d5afab3",
			"fileName": "uno.config.ts",
			"wiki": "The UnoCSS engine uses the loaded presets and shortcuts to generate CSS rules only for the classes that were found. It expands the `icon-btn` shortcut into its corresponding utilities and generates the necessary styles for the `i-carbon-campsite` icon via `presetIcons`.",
			"cellName": "On-Demand CSS Generation - uno.config.ts:L16-25",
			"cellId": "02652819-aa39-437a-a6f7-9b605d44708d",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 16,
			"endLine": 25,
			"parentCellId": "f7702ab9-b209-44eb-90f2-653042bc6568",
			"parentPath": "uno.config.ts",
