		"1f3fc838-1879-471d-9579-ca03b39028f8": {
			"path": "1f3fc838-1879-471d-9579-ca03b39028f8",
			"cellName": "I18n Build Configuration - vite.config.ts:L134-139",
			"cellId": "1f3fc838-1879-471d-9579-ca03b39028f8",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-2a0afe74-ff86-4420-9393-cfd780490955": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-2a0afe74-ff86-4420-9393-cfd780490955",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "During the build process, Vite configures the `unplugin-vue-i18n` plugin. This plugin is set up to find all locale files within the `locales/` directory, process them, and make them available for asynchronous (on-demand) loading in the application.",
			"cellName": "I18n Build Configuration - vite.config.ts:L134-139",
			"cellId": "1f3fc838-1879-471d-9579-ca03b39028f8",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 134,
			"endLine": 139,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "2a0afe74-ff86-4420-9393-cfd780490955"
				}
			]
		},
		"5412172c-3402-4c34-a157-f26563653acf": {
			"path": "5412172c-3402-4c34-a157-f26563653acf",
			"cellName": "Application Bootstrap: I18n Module Installation - i18n.ts:L47-50",
			"cellId": "5412172c-3402-4c34-a157-f26563653acf",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543"
		},
		"src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-d1d179fa-8999-45d4-a159-0700151b4011": {
			"path": "src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-d1d179fa-8999-45d4-a159-0700151b4011",
			"fileName": "i18n.ts",
			"wiki": "When the Vue application starts, it iterates through its modules. The `i18n` module's `install` function is executed, which registers the i18n instance with the Vue app and triggers the loading of the default language ('en').",
			"cellName": "Application Bootstrap: I18n Module Installation - i18n.ts:L47-50",
			"cellId": "5412172c-3402-4c34-a157-f26563653acf",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 47,
			"endLine": 50,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "d1d179fa-8999-45d4-a159-0700151b4011"
				}
			]
		},
		"82b3687d-d4ea-4a5d-b989-734892d1443c": {
			"path": "82b3687d-d4ea-4a5d-b989-734892d1443c",
			"cellName": "Asynchronously Load Default Locale - i18n.ts:L31-45",
			"cellId": "82b3687d-d4ea-4a5d-b989-734892d1443c",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543"
		},
		"src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-c7c38077-12e2-47cc-86c9-1954cba6b108": {
			"path": "src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-c7c38077-12e2-47cc-86c9-1954cba6b108",
			"fileName": "i18n.ts",
			"wiki": "The `loadLanguageAsync` function is called for the first time with 'en'. It discovers that this language has not been loaded yet. It uses a dynamic import (`localesMap[lang]()`) to fetch the contents of `locales/en.yml` asynchronously.",
			"cellName": "Asynchronously Load Default Locale - i18n.ts:L31-45",
			"cellId": "82b3687d-d4ea-4a5d-b989-734892d1443c",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 31,
			"endLine": 45,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "c7c38077-12e2-47cc-86c9-1954cba6b108"
				}
			]
		},
		"6b51377f-da10-4a41-af85-a0348b3e6b8e": {
			"path": "6b51377f-da10-4a41-af85-a0348b3e6b8e",
			"cellName": "Set Global Locale - i18n.ts:L24-29",
			"cellId": "6b51377f-da10-4a41-af85-a0348b3e6b8e",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543"
		},
		"src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-40821c64-5c66-4056-bce8-933e78cfe728": {
			"path": "src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-40821c64-5c66-4056-bce8-933e78cfe728",
			"fileName": "i18n.ts",
			"wiki": "After registering the messages, `setI18nLanguage` is called. This function updates the global `i18n.global.locale.value` to 'en' and sets the `lang` attribute of the `<html>` tag, making English the active language for the application.",
			"cellName": "Set Global Locale - i18n.ts:L24-29",
			"cellId": "6b51377f-da10-4a41-af85-a0348b3e6b8e",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 24,
			"endLine": 29,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "40821c64-5c66-4056-bce8-933e78cfe728"
				}
			]
		},
		"c499fbc7-dcf8-4a8b-b3e2-50615f93bb31": {
			"path": "c499fbc7-dcf8-4a8b-b3e2-50615f93bb31",
			"cellName": "Determine and Load Next Locale - TheFooter.vue:L6-12",
			"cellId": "c499fbc7-dcf8-4a8b-b3e2-50615f93bb31",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "f11c6eff-b35e-4490-8979-0196e1258d8d"
		},
		"src/components/TheFooter.vue-simstep-f5f418c3-2e43-4f23-b943-9a4b2de48d98": {
			"path": "src/components/TheFooter.vue-simstep-f5f418c3-2e43-4f23-b943-9a4b2de48d98",
			"fileName": "TheFooter.vue",
			"wiki": "The `toggleLocales` function in `TheFooter.vue` gets the list of available locales, determines the next locale in the cycle (e.g., 'fr' if the current is 'en'), and calls `loadLanguageAsync` with the new locale code.",
			"cellName": "Determine and Load Next Locale - TheFooter.vue:L6-12",
			"cellId": "c499fbc7-dcf8-4a8b-b3e2-50615f93bb31",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 6,
			"endLine": 12,
			"parentCellId": "f11c6eff-b35e-4490-8979-0196e1258d8d",
			"parentPath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "f5f418c3-2e43-4f23-b943-9a4b2de48d98"
				}
			]
		},
		"5015c125-9fdf-43ee-974c-65b29bdb02c7": {
			"path": "5015c125-9fdf-43ee-974c-65b29bdb02c7",
			"cellName": "Fetch and Register New Locale Messages - i18n.ts:L41-43",
			"cellId": "5015c125-9fdf-43ee-974c-65b29bdb02c7",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543"
		},
		"src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-f71ded1b-55e4-46ef-972e-f86d4c597ac7": {
			"path": "src/modules/i18n.ts-simstep-f71ded1b-55e4-46ef-972e-f86d4c597ac7",
			"fileName": "i18n.ts",
			"wiki": "The `loadLanguageAsync` function runs again, this time for 'fr'. It dynamically imports `locales/fr.yml`, then uses `i18n.global.setLocaleMessage` to add the French translations to the i18n instance and adds 'fr' to the `loadedLanguages` array.",
			"cellName": "Fetch and Register New Locale Messages - i18n.ts:L41-43",
			"cellId": "5015c125-9fdf-43ee-974c-65b29bdb02c7",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 41,
			"endLine": 43,
			"parentCellId": "ea8d6ea6-6a0d-4114-bf9d-ad284a502543",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "f71ded1b-55e4-46ef-972e-f86d4c597ac7"
				}
			]
		},
		"3026ea08-bb96-478c-9be1-c05638e8c471": {
			"path": "3026ea08-bb96-478c-9be1-c05638e8c471",
			"cellName": "UI Reactively Updates - TheFooter.vue:L11",
			"cellId": "3026ea08-bb96-478c-9be1-c05638e8c471",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "f11c6eff-b35e-4490-8979-0196e1258d8d"
		},
		"src/components/TheFooter.vue-simstep-45c19b04-c2ba-4f97-8501-a7d150772334": {
			"path": "src/components/TheFooter.vue-simstep-45c19b04-c2ba-4f97-8501-a7d150772334",
			"fileName": "TheFooter.vue",
			"wiki": "Back in `TheFooter.vue`, the `locale` ref obtained from `useI18n()` is updated to 'fr'. Because this ref is reactive, Vue's reactivity system automatically re-renders any part of the template that depends on it, such as tooltips using the `t()` function. For example, `t('button.home')` now resolves to 'Accueil' instead of 'Home'.",
			"cellName": "UI Reactively Updates - TheFooter.vue:L11",
			"cellId": "3026ea08-bb96-478c-9be1-c05638e8c471",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 11,
			"endLine": 11,
			"parentCellId": "f11c6eff-b35e-4490-8979-0196e1258d8d",
			"parentPath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
					"simStepId": "45c19b04-c2ba-4f97-8501-a7d150772334"
				}
			]
		},
		"5777d2a6-5cfa-4105-837b-765669323dd0": {
			"path": "5777d2a6-5cfa-4105-837b-765669323dd0",
			"cellName": "Vite Plugin\nInitialization",
			"cellId": "5777d2a6-5cfa-4105-837b-765669323dd0",
