		"b3b4ee60-e621-41d8-9708-7f0bd05da5ca": {
			"path": "b3b4ee60-e621-41d8-9708-7f0bd05da5ca",
			"cellName": "Build: Load Vite Configuration - vite.config.ts:L152-161",
			"cellId": "b3b4ee60-e621-41d8-9708-7f0bd05da5ca",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-55371288-f6df-481f-a218-ddc7aed45773": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-55371288-f6df-481f-a218-ddc7aed45773",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "The `pnpm build` command initiates the Vite build process. Vite loads `vite.config.ts`, which contains the configuration for Static Site Generation (SSG) via `vite-ssg`. The `ssgOptions` object defines how SSG will be performed, including script loading, formatting, critical CSS options, and a post-generation hook.",
			"cellName": "Build: Load Vite Configuration - vite.config.ts:L152-161",
			"cellId": "b3b4ee60-e621-41d8-9708-7f0bd05da5ca",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 152,
			"endLine": 161,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Static Site Generation (SSG) for Performance and SEO",
					"simStepId": "55371288-f6df-481f-a218-ddc7aed45773"
				}
			]
		},
		"5bf97fa8-8d70-4955-b5f9-0bbc76f5c531": {
			"path": "5bf97fa8-8d70-4955-b5f9-0bbc76f5c531",
			"cellName": "Build: Initialize Vue App with ViteSSG - main.ts:L13-17",
			"cellId": "5bf97fa8-8d70-4955-b5f9-0bbc76f5c531",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "b33cf786-b499-4506-b9d2-0f60ca79bdc6"
		},
		"src/main.ts-simstep-30e81ffb-c3d9-4814-8ff3-e4820cab536f": {
			"path": "src/main.ts-simstep-30e81ffb-c3d9-4814-8ff3-e4820cab536f",
			"fileName": "main.ts",
			"wiki": "The `vite-ssg` process finds and executes the `createApp` export from the entry point `src/main.ts`. This function configures `ViteSSG` with the root Vue component (`App.vue`), the application routes, and a callback function to install modules like Pinia and Vue I18n on the app instance.",
			"cellName": "Build: Initialize Vue App with ViteSSG - main.ts:L13-17",
			"cellId": "5bf97fa8-8d70-4955-b5f9-0bbc76f5c531",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 13,
			"endLine": 17,
			"parentCellId": "b33cf786-b499-4506-b9d2-0f60ca79bdc6",
			"parentPath": "src/main.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Static Site Generation (SSG) for Performance and SEO",
					"simStepId": "30e81ffb-c3d9-4814-8ff3-e4820cab536f"
				}
			]
		},
		"446b66f9-c54e-43ee-a14c-e64578aa9043": {
			"path": "446b66f9-c54e-43ee-a14c-e64578aa9043",
			"cellName": "Build: Populate Initial State via Pinia Module - pinia.ts:L6-17",
			"cellId": "446b66f9-c54e-43ee-a14c-e64578aa9043",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e"
		},
		"src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-08e11117-a6a4-463e-ac9c-fc955f2aaa9b": {
			"path": "src/modules/pinia.ts-simstep-08e11117-a6a4-463e-ac9c-fc955f2aaa9b",
			"fileName": "pinia.ts",
			"wiki": "The Pinia module (`src/modules/pinia.ts`) is executed. Since `isClient` is false, it populates `initialState.pinia` with the current state of all Pinia stores. This state will be serialized and embedded into the generated HTML to be hydrated on the client-side.",
			"cellName": "Build: Populate Initial State via Pinia Module - pinia.ts:L6-17",
			"cellId": "446b66f9-c54e-43ee-a14c-e64578aa9043",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 6,
			"endLine": 17,
			"parentCellId": "fdf4cf4a-94d1-4d99-b30f-c82df7c8749e",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/pinia.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Static Site Generation (SSG) for Performance and SEO",
					"simStepId": "08e11117-a6a4-463e-ac9c-fc955f2aaa9b"
				}
			]
		},
		"eb406743-fc1d-4133-86a3-534cb6e512e5": {
			"path": "eb406743-fc1d-4133-86a3-534cb6e512e5",
			"cellName": "Build: Inline Critical CSS - vite.config.ts:L155-157",
			"cellId": "eb406743-fc1d-4133-86a3-534cb6e512e5",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-41d3b6c4-93c7-495d-a2d8-aa844922bb3a": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-41d3b6c4-93c7-495d-a2d8-aa844922bb3a",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "For each rendered page, `vite-ssg` uses the 'beasties' tool to identify the CSS rules necessary for the initial viewport (critical CSS). These styles are then inlined into a `<style>` tag in the `<head>` of the final HTML document, ensuring the page renders content as quickly as possible without waiting for external stylesheets.",
			"cellName": "Build: Inline Critical CSS - vite.config.ts:L155-157",
			"cellId": "eb406743-fc1d-4133-86a3-534cb6e512e5",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 155,
			"endLine": 157,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Static Site Generation (SSG) for Performance and SEO",
					"simStepId": "41d3b6c4-93c7-495d-a2d8-aa844922bb3a"
				}
			]
		},
		"a4509451-8f0f-4e67-a894-400f99ee7830": {
			"path": "a4509451-8f0f-4e67-a894-400f99ee7830",
			"cellName": "Build: Generate Sitemap - vite.config.ts:L158-160",
			"cellId": "a4509451-8f0f-4e67-a894-400f99ee7830",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-4c6e794a-ff9f-4e39-80d6-11684d8190eb": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-4c6e794a-ff9f-4e39-80d6-11684d8190eb",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "The `onFinished` hook calls `generateSitemap()`. This function, provided by `vite-ssg-sitemap`, inspects the generated static files in the `dist` directory and creates a `sitemap.xml` file. This file lists all available pages, which helps search engines discover and index the site's content more effectively.",
			"cellName": "Build: Generate Sitemap - vite.config.ts:L158-160",
			"cellId": "a4509451-8f0f-4e67-a894-400f99ee7830",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 158,
			"endLine": 160,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Static Site Generation (SSG) for Performance and SEO",
					"simStepId": "4c6e794a-ff9f-4e39-80d6-11684d8190eb"
				}
			]
		},
