		"4547ad22-1b50-4478-be42-339d282f3431": {
			"path": "4547ad22-1b50-4478-be42-339d282f3431",
			"cellName": "PWA Plugin Configuration - vite.config.ts:L105-118",
			"cellId": "4547ad22-1b50-4478-be42-339d282f3431",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e"
		},
		"vite.config.ts-simstep-8977113e-252f-41ca-a0c1-6cbd00a12d9f": {
			"path": "vite.config.ts-simstep-8977113e-252f-41ca-a0c1-6cbd00a12d9f",
			"fileName": "vite.config.ts",
			"wiki": "The vite-plugin-pwa is configured in the main Vite configuration file. This setup defines the behavior of the Progressive Web App, including setting the service worker update strategy to 'autoUpdate' and specifying the contents of the web app manifest, such as the app's name, theme color, and icons.",
			"cellName": "PWA Plugin Configuration - vite.config.ts:L105-118",
			"cellId": "4547ad22-1b50-4478-be42-339d282f3431",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 105,
			"endLine": 118,
			"parentCellId": "ccc305be-cda4-4b7e-a555-b3a8456bb06e",
			"parentPath": "vite.config.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Progressive Web App (PWA) Readiness",
					"simStepId": "8977113e-252f-41ca-a0c1-6cbd00a12d9f"
				}
			]
		},
		"a1535fae-0236-4b23-869b-6cea75e98881": {
			"path": "a1535fae-0236-4b23-869b-6cea75e98881",
			"cellName": "App Initialization and Module Loading - main.ts:L21-22",
			"cellId": "a1535fae-0236-4b23-869b-6cea75e98881",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "b33cf786-b499-4506-b9d2-0f60ca79bdc6"
		},
		"src/main.ts-simstep-a21a1239-fa21-4117-b434-f5952242f9f5": {
			"path": "src/main.ts-simstep-a21a1239-fa21-4117-b434-f5952242f9f5",
			"fileName": "main.ts",
			"wiki": "The application's entry point, `main.ts`, uses ViteSSG to create the Vue app. It then dynamically imports all files from the `./modules` directory and executes their `install` function, passing in the application context. This modular approach ensures the PWA registration logic is automatically included.",
			"cellName": "App Initialization and Module Loading - main.ts:L21-22",
			"cellId": "a1535fae-0236-4b23-869b-6cea75e98881",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 21,
			"endLine": 22,
			"parentCellId": "b33cf786-b499-4506-b9d2-0f60ca79bdc6",
			"parentPath": "src/main.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Progressive Web App (PWA) Readiness",
					"simStepId": "a21a1239-fa21-4117-b434-f5952242f9f5"
				}
			]
		},
		"870c2550-81b8-4aad-b30a-77cbb2f30db1": {
			"path": "870c2550-81b8-4aad-b30a-77cbb2f30db1",
			"cellName": "Service Worker Registration - pwa.ts:L4-7",
			"cellId": "870c2550-81b8-4aad-b30a-77cbb2f30db1",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "0a964302-6743-4fb3-b28c-f90d366b0047"
		},
		"src/modules/pwa.ts-simstep-890ede66-7b9f-4956-bbba-10aba552f6da": {
			"path": "src/modules/pwa.ts-simstep-890ede66-7b9f-4956-bbba-10aba552f6da",
			"fileName": "pwa.ts",
			"wiki": "The `install` function in the PWA module checks if it's running on the client. If so, it waits for the Vue router to be ready, then dynamically imports the `registerSW` function from a virtual module provided by `vite-plugin-pwa`. It immediately calls this function to register the service worker in the browser, enabling offline capabilities and auto-updates.",
			"cellName": "Service Worker Registration - pwa.ts:L4-7",
			"cellId": "870c2550-81b8-4aad-b30a-77cbb2f30db1",
			"visible": true,
			"startLine": 4,
			"endLine": 7,
			"parentCellId": "0a964302-6743-4fb3-b28c-f90d366b0047",
			"parentPath": "src/modules/pwa.ts",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simulationKey": "Progressive Web App (PWA) Readiness",
					"simStepId": "890ede66-7b9f-4956-bbba-10aba552f6da"
				}
			]
		},
		"4ef967ed-f9f0-4597-a050-2be5b4ab6928": {
			"path": "4ef967ed-f9f0-4597-a050-2be5b4ab6928",
			"cellName": "HTML Icon and Manifest Linkage - index.html:L6",
			"cellId": "4ef967ed-f9f0-4597-a050-2be5b4ab6928",
			"visible": true,
			"parentCellId": "ffc31459-7cf5-40ac-a750-1673bc5e8e2b"
		},
		"index.html-simstep-53cb79e9-52fb-4dd0-9325-838ad08d830b": {
			"path": "index.html-simstep-53cb79e9-52fb-4dd0-9325-838ad08d830b",
			"fileName": "index.html",
			"wiki": "The main `index.html` file includes a link to the `pwa-192x192.png` icon for `apple-touch-icon` compatibility. During the build, `vite-plugin-pwa` also injects a `<link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.webmanifest\">` tag into the HTML head, allowing the browser to discover the web app's manifest file.",
			"cellName": "HTML Icon and Manifest Linkage - index.html:L6",
			"cellId": "4ef967ed-f9f0-4597-a050-2be5b4ab6928",
			"visible": true,
