			"description": "<ul><li>The application comes with Pinia, the official state management library for Vue, fully set up</li><li>- It provides a dedicated <code>src/stores</code> directory for organizing state modules</li><li>- A sample <code>user</li><li>ts</code> store demonstrates defining state, actions, and getters</li><li>- The setup includes integration with ViteSSG for state serialization during server-side generation, ensuring a seamless handoff to the client</li></ul>",
