					"simStepLabel": "UnoCSS Configuration Loading",
					"simStepDescription": "The UnoCSS Vite plugin automatically discovers and loads its configuration from `uno.config.ts`. This file defines crucial aspects like presets for utility classes (`presetUno`), icons (`presetIcons`), and custom shortcuts (`icon-btn`).",
