					"simStepLabel": "On-Demand CSS Generation",
					"simStepDescription": "The UnoCSS engine uses the loaded presets and shortcuts to generate CSS rules only for the classes that were found. It expands the `icon-btn` shortcut into its corresponding utilities and generates the necessary styles for the `i-carbon-campsite` icon via `presetIcons`.",
					"isEdge": 0,
