					"simStepLabel": "Virtual CSS Module Creation",
					"simStepDescription": "The UnoCSS Vite plugin creates a virtual module named `uno.css` that contains all the on-demand CSS rules. This virtual module can be imported like a regular CSS file in the application's source code.",
