			"description": "<ul><li>Vitesse uses UnoCSS for a high-performance, utility-first styling experience</li><li>- It generates CSS on-demand, meaning only the styles you actually use are included in the final bundle, keeping it small</li><li>- The configuration in <code>uno</li><li>config</li><li>ts</code> allows for custom shortcuts and themes</li><li>- It includes an icon preset, allowing developers to use thousands of icons from Iconify directly in their HTML with simple class names</li></ul>",
