		"Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)": {
			"name": "Out-of-the-Box Internationalization (I18n)",
			"simSteps": [
				{
					"simStepId": "2a0afe74-ff86-4420-9393-cfd780490955",
					"diagramNodeId": "1f3fc838-1879-471d-9579-ca03b39028f8",
					"simStepLabel": "I18n Build Configuration",
					"simStepDescription": "During the build process, Vite configures the `unplugin-vue-i18n` plugin. This plugin is set up to find all locale files within the `locales/` directory, process them, and make them available for asynchronous (on-demand) loading in the application.",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "vite.config.ts",
						"startLine": "134",
						"endLine": "139",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"VueI18n"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"runtimeOnly\": true,\n  \"compositionOnly\": true,\n  \"fullInstall\": true,\n  \"include\": \"/path/to/project/locales/**\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "b98a2d6c-375e-47d8-8310-fc104ce9981d",
					"diagramNodeId": "5777d2a6-5cfa-4105-837b-765669323dd0",
					"simStepLabel": "Vite Plugin Initialization",
					"simStepDescription": "The configuration for `unplugin-vue-i18n` is passed to the Vite build process, which prepares the environment for handling internationalization resources.",
					"isEdge": 1,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "vite.config.ts",
						"startLine": "134",
						"endLine": "139",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"VueI18n"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"runtimeOnly\": true,\n  \"compositionOnly\": true,\n  \"fullInstall\": true,\n  \"include\": \"/path/to/project/locales/**\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"runtimeOnly\": true,\n  \"compositionOnly\": true,\n  \"fullInstall\": true,\n  \"include\": \"/path/to/project/locales/**\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "d1d179fa-8999-45d4-a159-0700151b4011",
					"diagramNodeId": "5412172c-3402-4c34-a157-f26563653acf",
					"simStepLabel": "Application Bootstrap: I18n Module Installation",
					"simStepDescription": "When the Vue application starts, it iterates through its modules. The `i18n` module's `install` function is executed, which registers the i18n instance with the Vue app and triggers the loading of the default language ('en').",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "47",
						"endLine": "50",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"install",
							"app",
							"i18n"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"app\": \"<Vue App Instance>\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "122fd65c-9e7e-462d-a1ea-cb777fc4ad0b",
					"diagramNodeId": "3da79f04-d621-43e0-82cd-3271f7a3176b",
					"simStepLabel": "Initial Language Loading Trigger",
					"simStepDescription": "The `install` function calls `loadLanguageAsync` with 'en' to set the application's default language.",
					"isEdge": 1,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "49",
						"endLine": "49",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"loadLanguageAsync"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "c7c38077-12e2-47cc-86c9-1954cba6b108",
					"diagramNodeId": "82b3687d-d4ea-4a5d-b989-734892d1443c",
					"simStepLabel": "Asynchronously Load Default Locale",
					"simStepDescription": "The `loadLanguageAsync` function is called for the first time with 'en'. It discovers that this language has not been loaded yet. It uses a dynamic import (`localesMap[lang]()`) to fetch the contents of `locales/en.yml` asynchronously.",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "31",
						"endLine": "45",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"loadLanguageAsync",
							"localesMap",
							"loadedLanguages",
							"messages"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"default\": {\n    \"button\": {\n      \"about\": \"About\",\n      \"back\": \"Back\",\n      \"go\": \"GO\",\n      \"home\": \"Home\",\n      \"toggle_dark\": \"Toggle dark mode\",\n      \"toggle_langs\": \"Change languages\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "07a37f0f-e680-45ba-b71d-42963bc02b0a",
					"diagramNodeId": "c7f125c6-62a0-45df-ab41-a2bcbe12d132",
					"simStepLabel": "Pass Locale Data to I18n Instance",
					"simStepDescription": "The loaded message content from the YAML file is passed to the i18n instance to be registered.",
					"isEdge": 1,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "42",
						"endLine": "42",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"i18n.global.setLocaleMessage",
							"messages.default"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\",\n  \"messages\": {\n    \"button\": {\n      \"about\": \"About\",\n      \"back\": \"Back\",\n      \"go\": \"GO\",\n      \"home\": \"Home\",\n      \"toggle_dark\": \"Toggle dark mode\",\n      \"toggle_langs\": \"Change languages\"\n    }\n  }\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\",\n  \"messages\": {\n    \"button\": {\n      \"about\": \"About\",\n      \"back\": \"Back\",\n      \"go\": \"GO\",\n      \"home\": \"Home\",\n      \"toggle_dark\": \"Toggle dark mode\",\n      \"toggle_langs\": \"Change languages\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "40821c64-5c66-4056-bce8-933e78cfe728",
					"diagramNodeId": "6b51377f-da10-4a41-af85-a0348b3e6b8e",
					"simStepLabel": "Set Global Locale",
					"simStepDescription": "After registering the messages, `setI18nLanguage` is called. This function updates the global `i18n.global.locale.value` to 'en' and sets the `lang` attribute of the `<html>` tag, making English the active language for the application.",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "24",
						"endLine": "29",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"setI18nLanguage",
							"i18n.global.locale"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "cb1bdd6d-f932-4b59-86c6-02ecd69a0d82",
					"diagramNodeId": "4fe0efe8-f5a2-441b-854b-f2e5bbb1c08d",
					"simStepLabel": "User Clicks Language Toggle",
					"simStepDescription": "The user interacts with the UI by clicking the language toggle button in `TheFooter` component, which triggers the `toggleLocales` function.",
					"isEdge": 1,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
						"startLine": "1",
						"endLine": "14",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"toggleLocales"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"event\": \"click\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"event\": \"click\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "f5f418c3-2e43-4f23-b943-9a4b2de48d98",
					"diagramNodeId": "c499fbc7-dcf8-4a8b-b3e2-50615f93bb31",
					"simStepLabel": "Determine and Load Next Locale",
					"simStepDescription": "The `toggleLocales` function in `TheFooter.vue` gets the list of available locales, determines the next locale in the cycle (e.g., 'fr' if the current is 'en'), and calls `loadLanguageAsync` with the new locale code.",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
						"startLine": "6",
						"endLine": "12",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"toggleLocales",
							"availableLocales",
							"locale",
							"newLocale",
							"loadLanguageAsync"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"currentLocale\": \"en\",\n  \"availableLocales\": [\"ar\", \"de\", \"en\", \"es\", \"fr\", ...]\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"newLocale\": \"fr\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "21d295ac-d411-464b-93a4-e72988b3350c",
					"diagramNodeId": "f8937380-ea4d-476c-b164-5457e734c79d",
					"simStepLabel": "Trigger Asynchronous Loading of New Locale",
					"simStepDescription": "The new locale code ('fr') is passed to the `loadLanguageAsync` function to fetch and apply the new language.",
					"isEdge": 1,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
						"startLine": "10",
						"endLine": "10",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"loadLanguageAsync",
							"newLocale"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"fr\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"fr\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "f71ded1b-55e4-46ef-972e-f86d4c597ac7",
					"diagramNodeId": "5015c125-9fdf-43ee-974c-65b29bdb02c7",
					"simStepLabel": "Fetch and Register New Locale Messages",
					"simStepDescription": "The `loadLanguageAsync` function runs again, this time for 'fr'. It dynamically imports `locales/fr.yml`, then uses `i18n.global.setLocaleMessage` to add the French translations to the i18n instance and adds 'fr' to the `loadedLanguages` array.",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "41",
						"endLine": "43",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"localesMap",
							"messages",
							"i18n.global.setLocaleMessage",
							"loadedLanguages"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"fr\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"default\": {\n    \"button\": {\n      \"about\": \"À propos\",\n      \"back\": \"Retour\",\n      \"go\": \"ALLER\",\n      \"home\": \"Accueil\",\n      \"toggle_dark\": \"Changer le thème\",\n      \"toggle_langs\": \"Changer de langue\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "a17b4a0f-e8bb-499a-8c1c-6dded30396c4",
					"diagramNodeId": "10e78684-ffc6-492d-b256-cc18fdc557eb",
					"simStepLabel": "Update Global Locale Value",
					"simStepDescription": "The `loadLanguageAsync` function completes by calling `setI18nLanguage` with the new locale, 'fr'. This sets the reactive `i18n.global.locale.value` which will trigger updates in any component using it.",
					"isEdge": 1,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/modules/i18n.ts",
						"startLine": "44",
						"endLine": "44",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"setI18nLanguage"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"fr\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"lang\": \"fr\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"simStepId": "45c19b04-c2ba-4f97-8501-a7d150772334",
					"diagramNodeId": "3026ea08-bb96-478c-9be1-c05638e8c471",
					"simStepLabel": "UI Reactively Updates",
					"simStepDescription": "Back in `TheFooter.vue`, the `locale` ref obtained from `useI18n()` is updated to 'fr'. Because this ref is reactive, Vue's reactivity system automatically re-renders any part of the template that depends on it, such as tooltips using the `t()` function. For example, `t('button.home')` now resolves to 'Accueil' instead of 'Home'.",
					"isEdge": 0,
					"sourceCodeMapping": {
						"filePath": "src/components/TheFooter.vue",
						"startLine": "11",
						"endLine": "11",
						"relevantVariables": [
							"locale.value",
							"t"
						]
					},
					"inputDataExample": "{\n  \"newLocale\": \"fr\"\n}",
					"outputDataExample": "{\n  \"title\": \"Accueil\"\n}"
				}
			],
			"description": "<ul><li>The template is pre-configured for building multi-language applications</li><li>- It uses <code>vue-i18n</code> and provides a <code>/locales</code> directory where translation strings are managed in simple YAML files</li><li>- Language files are loaded asynchronously to optimize initial page load performance</li><li>- A language switching control is demonstrated in <code>TheFooter</li><li>vue</code> component</li></ul>",
			"simulationNodesAndEdges": {
				"1f3fc838-1879-471d-9579-ca03b39028f8": {
