					"simStepLabel": "E2E Test Flow: Handle Input and Navigate",
					"simStepDescription": "The 'Enter' keypress triggers the `go` function in the `index.vue` page. This function reads the name from the input field and uses the Vue Router to programmatically navigate to the dynamic route `/hi/Vitesse`.",
