			"description": "<ul><li>A comprehensive testing environment is set up from the start to encourage good development practices</li><li>- It includes Vitest for fast, Vite-native unit and component testing</li><li>- Cypress is configured for end-to-end (E2E) testing, with example tests for basic navigation and interaction</li><li>- A CI workflow file for GitHub Actions is provided to automate testing on push and pull requests</li></ul>",
